ResponsePay is a lightweight mobile bitcoin payment solution [[eWallet]] built with responsive & adaptive web design and will scale to fit. ResponsePay provides people with a simple yet very effective method of sending bitcoin locally and internationally. ResponsePay can reach almost all mobile phones, and it is instant.

